  <SourceScript>k__BackingField: "Plucky: Um\u2026 hi? \r\n\r\nPlucky: (Gosh I\u2019m
    so nervous I\u2019ve never ordered from one of these places?) \r\n\r\nPlucky:
    Sorry uh, can I get\u2026 \r\n\r\nPlucky: Uhhhhh\u2026 \r\n\r\nPlucky: Hold on,
    can I get a\u2026 \r\n\r\nPlucky: ...\r\n\r\nPlucky: Umm\u2026 oh yeah! \r\n\r\nPlucky:
    A healing potion! \r\n\r\nPlucky: If you could make one of those for me, I\u2019d
    super appreciate it\u2026 \r\n\r\nPlucky: I used to have pretty high stats\u2026
    \n\nPlucky: but then I got cursed to lose all of my EXP...\r\n\r\nPlucky: I\u2019m
    going out on an adventuring quest today. \n\nPlucky: For the first time. In a
    while. All the way back at Lv. 1\u2026\r\n\r\nPlucky: But yeah\u2026 if you could
    make a healing potion I\u2019d really appreciate it\u2026\r\n"
